                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">数据分析都很到位，得出的结论就乐观得让人呵呵了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="782336291">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-782336291" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-782336291" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="782336291">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinkai719/">阅微草堂</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-03-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">美国的政治和文化的民主其实仅仅是表象。本文核心是美国经济不平等的政治原因</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
